      </div>
      <div class="col">
      <p class="heading">Great Wall Of China</p>
      <p class="content">The Great Wall of China is one of the most notorious structures in the entire world. The Jinshanling section in Hebei Province, China, pictured here, is only a small part of the wall that stretches over 4,000 kilometers (2,500 miles).</p>
      <button class="buttons"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Great_Wall_of_China"><i class="fa fa-search" aria-hidden="true"></i> About Great Wall of China</a></button>
      </div>
      
